HEADWORD: Roster
<hw>Ros"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Perhaps a corruption
of <ets>register</ets>; or cf. <ets>roll</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Mil.)</fld>
<def>A register or roll showing the order in which officers, enlisted
men, companies, or regiments are called on to serve.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

